<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Confirmation de votre adresse e-mail</title>
		{# Tailwind CSS via CDN for email compatibility. This is the safest approach for emails. #}
		<link href="https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			/* Fallback styles for email clients that don't fully support Tailwind */
			body {
				font-family: sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.header {
				background-color: #f7fafc; /* gray-50 */
				padding: 20px;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.content {
				background-color: #ffffff; /* white */
				padding: 30px;
				border-radius: 8px;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 12px 24px;
				background-color: #3B82F6; /* blue-500 */
				color: #ffffff !important;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 0.375rem; /* rounded-md */
				font-weight: 600; /* font-semibold */
			}
			.button:hover {
				background-color: #2563EB; /* blue-600 */
			}
			.footer {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 20px;
				font-size: 0.875rem; /* text-sm */
				color: #6B7280; /* gray-500 */
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-100 text-coffee">
		<div class="container mx-auto p-4 sm:p-8">
			<div class="header bg-gray-50 rounded-t-lg">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-coffee my-4">Confirmez votre adresse e-mail !</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="content bg-white shadow-lg rounded-b-lg p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
				<p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
					Bonjour !
				</p>
				<p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
					Veuillez confirmer votre adresse e-mail en cliquant sur le lien ci-dessous :
				</p>
				<div class="text-center">
					<a href="{{ signedUrl|raw }}" class="button block w-fit mx-auto">
						Confirmer mon e-mail
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center mt-4">
					Ce lien expirera dans
					{{ expiresAtMessageKey|trans(expiresAtMessageData, 'VerifyEmailBundle') }}.
				</p>
				<p class="text-base leading-relaxed mt-6">
					À bientôt !
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer mt-6">
				<p>Cet e-mail a été envoyé automatiquement. Merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
